data.description: Fantastic move in ready 4 bdrm 2 bath ranch on 1 acre of flat land. This updated home features granite countertops in kitchen and bathroom, all brand new kitchen appliances, gas fireplace, hardwood flooring, fresh paint, new lvp flooring in all bedrooms (no carpet!) , above ground pool with freshly stained deck & nicely sized shed. Large 6-8 person tornado shelter is rated to withstand an ef5 tornado & will remain with the home! Huge deck around the pool is great for entertaining. This beautiful yard backs up to a farm and sits just outside city limits in a quiet neighborhood with NO HOA! Easy access to amenities like restaurants and shopping and the Nashville commute.
